      "amount": "for frying",
      "notes": "for frying fritters"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oil for frying to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Whisk together eggs, milk, and melted butter in a bowl.",
    "Add flour and mix until just combined.",
    "Gently fold in softened brie cheese.",
    "If desired, add chopped herbs or chives.",
    "Dust fritter mix with a small amount of flour.",
    "Using a piping bag or spoon, drop rounded fritters into hot oil.",
    "Fry for 2-3 minutes, until golden brown.",
    "Drain on paper towels and serve warm.",
    "Brush with additional melted butter if desired."
